WEBVTT

01:38.150 --> 01:40.750
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.400 --> 01:43.630
[Episode 17]

01:45.120 --> 01:46.320
Eat it while it's hot.

01:47.039 --> 01:47.680
That one's burnt.

01:47.680 --> 01:48.410
Don't eat it.

01:49.680 --> 01:50.280
It's fine.

01:50.759 --> 01:51.820
I like it like this.

01:55.280 --> 01:55.759
Senior,

01:56.280 --> 01:58.000
I went to a nearby village just now

01:58.000 --> 01:58.920
and paid them

01:59.039 --> 02:01.000
to have them draw a map of North Xiang.

02:01.000 --> 02:02.790
There are 3 roads to North Xiang.

02:02.790 --> 02:03.790
There is only 1 official road

02:03.790 --> 02:05.250
for traveling merchants—

02:05.480 --> 02:06.790
that is this road on the south.

02:06.790 --> 02:07.990
But it's a bit further

02:08.150 --> 02:09.750
and passes through 2 cliffs.

02:10.030 --> 02:11.490
The north road is shorter,

02:11.840 --> 02:13.240
but it's all sandy paths—

02:13.470 --> 02:14.330
hard to travel.

02:15.240 --> 02:16.590
There is also a west road.

02:16.590 --> 02:18.150
It's longer than the north road,

02:18.150 --> 02:19.840
but connects to half of the official road,

02:19.840 --> 02:20.960
making it relatively easier to travel.

02:20.960 --> 02:21.310
Okay.

02:21.520 --> 02:23.079
Then let's head west.

02:31.710 --> 02:32.190
Senior,

02:32.800 --> 02:34.030
do you know
where the person you're looking for

02:34.030 --> 02:34.870
exactly is?

02:35.590 --> 02:37.030
North Xiang is vast with many cities.

02:37.030 --> 02:38.370
If we search one by one,

02:38.400 --> 02:40.360
I'm afraid it'll take
more than half a year.

02:40.360 --> 02:41.310
Master is still waiting for us

02:41.310 --> 02:42.120
at the sect.

02:42.840 --> 02:43.400
I know.

02:44.079 --> 02:45.280
But I have to find him.

02:45.700 --> 02:46.360
I can't remember

02:46.360 --> 02:47.160
anything now.

02:47.630 --> 02:48.960
That darn official said

02:49.000 --> 02:50.710
I married him in Wei County

02:51.240 --> 02:53.280
and killed someone for him in the capital.

02:53.280 --> 02:55.010
But I don't remember anything.

02:55.430 --> 02:55.960
So,

02:56.360 --> 02:57.190
he must have done something

02:57.190 --> 02:58.310
to me in the dark.

02:59.520 --> 03:00.310
When we met last time,

03:00.310 --> 03:01.970
I felt he wasn't a good person.

03:02.030 --> 03:03.590
Seeing how beautiful you are,

03:03.590 --> 03:05.190
he must've tricked you into marrying him

03:05.190 --> 03:07.400
and decided to use you
after taking advantage of you.

03:07.400 --> 03:08.470
He deserves to die.

03:08.710 --> 03:09.710
He's terrible.

03:09.910 --> 03:10.370
Well...

03:10.840 --> 03:12.300
That might not be the case.

03:13.520 --> 03:14.670
I can kinda guess

03:14.870 --> 03:16.150
why I married him.

03:17.150 --> 03:18.560
When I left the sect,

03:18.850 --> 03:20.190
I had the thought
of finding a death row prisoner

03:20.190 --> 03:21.000
to marry.

03:21.910 --> 03:22.840
Do you remember—

03:23.280 --> 03:25.030
I have the destiny
of bringing death to my husbands.

03:25.030 --> 03:26.940
I am destined
to bring death to 3 husbands.

03:26.940 --> 03:28.230
So I wanted to find

03:28.260 --> 03:30.320
a heinous death row prisoner to marry

03:30.360 --> 03:31.620
to break this destiny.

03:32.430 --> 03:33.400
I guess

03:33.840 --> 03:34.750
I found him,

03:35.120 --> 03:36.579
and after marrying him,

03:36.800 --> 03:38.590
I found out he was a good person,

03:39.100 --> 03:41.160
so I went to the capital to avenge him.

03:43.520 --> 03:44.120
Oh, right.

03:44.590 --> 03:45.680
Didn't Emperor Zong Ding

03:45.680 --> 03:46.540
exonerate him?

03:47.079 --> 03:47.840
It shows

03:48.000 --> 03:48.960
he was wronged.

03:49.240 --> 03:50.800
And the Landlady also said

03:51.120 --> 03:53.360
I was brought back to the inn
after he saved me.

03:53.360 --> 03:54.790
With my skills,

03:55.040 --> 03:56.190
it would be impossible
to retreat unscathed

03:56.190 --> 03:57.840
under the siege of various immortal sects

03:57.840 --> 03:58.700
in the capital.

03:59.360 --> 04:00.560
He must have saved me.

04:01.280 --> 04:01.870
So?

04:02.150 --> 04:02.840
So—

04:03.520 --> 04:05.250
that's where the problem lies.

04:05.750 --> 04:07.010
Since he is so capable,

04:07.400 --> 04:08.470
why would he willingly

04:08.470 --> 04:09.280
suffer

04:09.560 --> 04:11.560
and endure death by a thousand cuts?

04:11.560 --> 04:13.220
And why did he erase my memory?

04:13.680 --> 04:15.150
He is obviously very capable.

04:15.150 --> 04:16.290
Even if I knew the truth

04:16.290 --> 04:18.920
and turned against him,
I couldn't have beaten him.

04:18.920 --> 04:21.350
I guess he just didn't want to hurt me.

04:22.310 --> 04:23.710
And in Chongling Valley,

04:23.800 --> 04:25.530
he saved my life several times.

04:25.770 --> 04:26.770
He was the one

04:26.800 --> 04:28.360
who gave me my Gongshan Jade Tablet.

04:28.360 --> 04:29.820
He was an honest official,

04:30.000 --> 04:31.200
cared for the people,

04:31.460 --> 04:32.409
and has powerful skills,

04:32.409 --> 04:34.270
yet he doesn't seek immortality.

04:34.390 --> 04:35.790
I really can't figure out

04:35.800 --> 04:37.000
what a person like him

04:37.560 --> 04:38.310
could possibly want

04:38.310 --> 04:39.720
from me.

04:40.800 --> 04:41.720
Didn't you just say

04:41.720 --> 04:43.390
you wanted an explanation from him?

04:43.390 --> 04:43.870
Yes.

04:44.390 --> 04:45.920
You want to settle scores with him?

04:45.920 --> 04:46.270
Yes.

04:47.510 --> 04:48.190
But look at

04:48.190 --> 04:49.870
the words you just used to describe him.

04:49.870 --> 04:51.120
Calling him an honest official

04:51.120 --> 04:52.120
not seeking fame—

04:52.120 --> 04:53.000
a hidden master

04:53.000 --> 04:54.260
with powerful skills.

04:54.360 --> 04:54.820
Senior,

04:55.560 --> 04:57.950
are you really trying to
settle scores with him?

04:57.950 --> 04:59.610
Good people do bad things too.

04:59.870 --> 05:00.530
Besides...

05:01.070 --> 05:01.830
Besides, I need to get

05:01.830 --> 05:02.690
my memory back.

05:09.240 --> 05:11.120
[Qinghong Sect Headquarters]

05:16.800 --> 05:17.480
Master summoned

05:17.480 --> 05:19.140
us Dharma Kings for a meeting.

05:19.360 --> 05:20.890
Why is a Vajra like you here?

05:22.310 --> 05:24.040
He is no ordinary Vajra.

05:24.700 --> 05:25.600
She serves day and night

05:25.600 --> 05:27.200
by the Master's side.

05:26.140 --> 05:28.700
[Qinghong Sect, Dharma King Niankong]
[Qinghong Sect, Dharma King Wenyin]

05:27.600 --> 05:29.060
Thoughtfulness like this

05:29.070 --> 05:31.130
isn't something everyone can learn.

05:32.070 --> 05:32.920
Fortunately

05:33.360 --> 05:35.600
our sect ranks by

05:35.600 --> 05:36.630
the strength of our magic.

05:36.630 --> 05:38.290
If we ranked by anything else,

05:38.720 --> 05:40.580
I'm afraid we'd both fall behind.

05:42.560 --> 05:45.190
If Dharma King Wenyin would like to learn
some of "anything else,"

05:45.190 --> 05:46.070
I can teach you.

06:06.290 --> 06:10.400
[Qinghong Sect, Lord Tiling]

06:13.360 --> 06:14.920
Master told you to come in.

06:31.790 --> 06:34.510
[Qinghong Sect, Lord Baori]

06:39.000 --> 06:41.130
The Phoenix God's power is unmatched;

06:41.360 --> 06:43.270
long live, Master!

06:43.710 --> 06:46.780
[Qinghong Sect, Futian]

06:49.390 --> 06:50.510
Rise, everyone.

06:50.800 --> 06:51.860
Thank you, Master.

06:57.159 --> 07:00.160
Bishui Branch suffered heavy losses
this time.

07:01.120 --> 07:03.680
Hewabu and many cultists

07:04.240 --> 07:07.640
died because they were controlled by
the Spell of Utterance.

07:08.190 --> 07:09.800
I invited you here today

07:10.150 --> 07:10.880
for that—

07:10.910 --> 07:11.380
Master.

07:12.310 --> 07:13.630
Over the years, Hewabu

07:13.910 --> 07:14.910
has been loyal

07:15.360 --> 07:17.360
and protected thousands of
our sect members.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.420
Now that he is dead,

07:18.480 --> 07:20.190
we must avenge him.

07:21.950 --> 07:22.560
Xunmu.

07:24.160 --> 07:25.240
You speak first.

07:31.920 --> 07:32.630
Master.

07:33.600 --> 07:34.800
When I went to the capital,

07:34.800 --> 07:36.070
I saw the cultivator

07:36.070 --> 07:37.130
who killed Mr. Gui.

07:37.360 --> 07:38.920
I exchanged a few moves with her

07:38.920 --> 07:39.950
and she ran away.

07:41.800 --> 07:43.430
You couldn't even stop

07:44.270 --> 07:46.000
a mere Qi Refining cultivator?

07:46.159 --> 07:47.820
You have no idea, Dharma King.

07:48.600 --> 07:50.240
There is nothing special

07:50.240 --> 07:51.240
about this cultivator.

07:51.240 --> 07:52.330
It's just that

07:52.360 --> 07:53.690
she's aided by a master.

07:54.120 --> 07:55.320
With just a few moves,

07:55.610 --> 07:56.430
he could make the Heavenly Talents

07:56.430 --> 07:58.290
of major immortal sects back off.

07:58.560 --> 07:59.190
I suspect

07:59.750 --> 08:01.280
it was also him who wiped out

08:01.680 --> 08:02.540
Bishui Branch.

08:04.800 --> 08:07.200
Killing a few Heavenly Talents is nothing.

08:09.770 --> 08:10.400
Master.

08:10.950 --> 08:13.430
I volunteer to go to Bishui Branch

08:13.630 --> 08:15.230
to look for this cultivator.

08:15.430 --> 08:16.490
I will use her blood

08:16.720 --> 08:18.680
as a sacrifice to our Phoenix God.

08:22.600 --> 08:23.830
If so,

08:24.830 --> 08:25.720
you may go.

08:33.000 --> 08:34.000
You may all leave.

08:39.200 --> 08:40.200
Vajra Xunmu.

08:42.320 --> 08:42.870
Master.

08:43.150 --> 08:45.080
Go along with Wenyin.

08:45.840 --> 08:46.840
Keep an eye on him.

08:47.600 --> 08:50.000
Don't let him cause trouble.

08:51.480 --> 08:52.000
Yes.

09:04.440 --> 09:06.550
The Bishui Branch is a trivial matter.

09:06.550 --> 09:08.480
Our business is what's important.

09:08.600 --> 09:10.200
The Central Plains replied,

09:10.240 --> 09:11.750
saying the person has arrived.

09:11.750 --> 09:12.210
Master,

09:12.870 --> 09:14.070
you must be prepared.

09:27.870 --> 09:29.730
Once I get the money in Xutuo City,

09:30.150 --> 09:31.750
I will leave here immediately.

09:31.750 --> 09:34.080
I won't stay here for even another moment!

09:34.480 --> 09:35.510
This place is no good.

09:35.510 --> 09:36.240
It's too dry.

09:36.870 --> 09:38.930
It's not a place for humans to live in.

09:39.440 --> 09:40.840
They owe me a lot of money.

09:41.120 --> 09:42.450
I have to get it all back.

09:42.480 --> 09:44.720
They'd better not think they can get
even a single cent from me.

09:44.720 --> 09:45.580
On the way back,

09:45.790 --> 09:47.120
as soon as we leave this desert

09:47.120 --> 09:48.480
and reach a place
where I can hire a carriage,

09:48.480 --> 09:50.010
I'll hire one immediately.

09:50.200 --> 09:51.790
I won't walk back no matter what.

09:51.790 --> 09:53.850
I'll go to Zuixian Restaurant first.

09:53.960 --> 09:55.150
It's for nothing else

09:55.150 --> 09:57.120
but those soy-braised pork trotters.

09:57.120 --> 09:58.750
Then I'll go to the Textile Pavilion

09:58.750 --> 10:00.410
to get a new pair of boots made.

10:08.440 --> 10:09.000
Lu.

10:09.510 --> 10:10.840
Are you going to stay in North Xiang

10:10.840 --> 10:12.640
or go back to the Central Plains?

10:16.270 --> 10:16.670
Lu?

10:17.960 --> 10:19.020
Did he fall asleep?

10:19.470 --> 10:21.670
You can sleep even when it's this bumpy?

10:23.550 --> 10:24.550
Stop, stop!

10:26.320 --> 10:27.000
Slowly.

10:27.360 --> 10:27.870
Come on.

10:28.390 --> 10:28.840
Okay.

10:30.080 --> 10:30.880
Gosh, my back.

10:33.030 --> 10:33.720
Let's rest a bit.

10:33.720 --> 10:34.120
Yeah.

10:34.870 --> 10:35.600
Help massage me.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.330
He's asleep.

10:36.550 --> 10:38.150
No wonder he wasn't answering.

10:38.150 --> 10:39.480
This coffin lid is so thick.

10:39.480 --> 10:40.670
I'll leave a crack open for you

10:40.670 --> 10:41.800
So you can cool down.

10:50.480 --> 10:51.080
Sir,

10:51.630 --> 10:52.750
what song are you singing?

10:52.750 --> 10:53.720
The Boat Song.

10:54.510 --> 10:55.690
You are from North Xiang—

10:55.690 --> 10:56.960
have you ever seen a boat?

10:56.960 --> 10:58.150
Yet you sing a song about boats?

10:58.150 --> 10:58.950
How ignorant.

10:59.600 --> 11:01.480
Boats don't just sail on the water.

11:01.480 --> 11:03.410
There are also boats in the desert.

11:05.030 --> 11:06.480
Boats in the desert?

11:08.320 --> 11:09.320
Flying boats.

11:09.510 --> 11:10.200
Those boats

11:10.360 --> 11:11.560
are over 30 feet tall,

11:11.870 --> 11:13.000
with dozens of rooms

11:13.240 --> 11:15.000
and can hold hundreds of people.

11:15.000 --> 11:15.930
From a distance,

11:16.000 --> 11:17.930
it looks like a pavilion in the air.

11:18.240 --> 11:20.900
It's much bigger
than your Zuixian Restaurant.

11:23.090 --> 11:24.150
I don't believe it.

11:24.790 --> 11:25.450
Me neither.

11:26.000 --> 11:27.460
You're talking nonsense.

11:28.120 --> 11:28.850
What's that?

11:30.080 --> 11:31.440
What's going on?

11:37.200 --> 11:38.130
What's going on?

11:38.270 --> 11:39.510
There's a large group of people on horses

11:39.510 --> 11:40.310
300 feet away.

11:40.750 --> 11:41.630
They're after us.

11:41.630 --> 11:41.960
Who?

11:42.200 --> 11:43.060
Who's after us?

11:43.240 --> 11:44.150
Mounted bandits?

11:44.150 --> 11:45.350
They're coming fast.

11:45.440 --> 11:46.040
It's them.

11:46.260 --> 11:47.080
They're just some mounted bandits.

11:47.080 --> 11:48.540
We can just fight them off.

11:49.120 --> 11:50.000
My divine sword

11:50.360 --> 11:51.550
finally has a use.

11:52.200 --> 11:53.510
There are too many of them. We can't win.

11:53.510 --> 11:54.040
Let's go!

11:54.480 --> 11:55.200
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

11:55.200 --> 11:55.910
Hurry up.

11:56.360 --> 11:56.690
Come.

11:58.240 --> 11:58.700
Master!

11:59.390 --> 12:00.080
Master!

12:01.430 --> 12:02.440
Didn't you hire me

12:02.440 --> 12:03.360
to protect you?

12:04.870 --> 12:07.070
Why run from some mere mounted bandits?

12:07.440 --> 12:08.360
Wait for me.

12:12.790 --> 12:13.650
Where are they?

12:17.120 --> 12:18.270
Old man.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.480
My parents died

12:21.510 --> 12:22.550
over 50 years ago.

12:23.390 --> 12:25.150
Here you are
saying there's going to be a disaster.

12:25.150 --> 12:26.010
What disaster?

12:26.960 --> 12:27.390
What?

12:28.320 --> 12:30.120
Are you going to move the graves?

12:31.120 --> 12:32.050
What's going on?

12:32.720 --> 12:33.320
Exactly.

12:34.080 --> 12:34.940
How about this?

12:35.270 --> 12:36.930
See if you can read my fortune.

12:37.390 --> 12:38.670
If you can,

12:37.570 --> 12:40.820
[Shi Wen]

12:39.570 --> 12:40.990
I'll admit you're good.

12:41.330 --> 12:43.280
[Tai Shiqian]

12:42.510 --> 12:43.200
Okay.

12:43.870 --> 12:44.960
If I'm right,

12:45.080 --> 12:46.810
you can't go back on your words.

12:47.630 --> 12:49.030
And what if you're wrong?

12:49.510 --> 12:51.960
I'll smash your darn stall today.

12:52.870 --> 12:53.960
Deal.

12:59.750 --> 13:01.550
Your forehead is dark—

13:01.870 --> 13:03.800
it's a sign of impending disaster.

13:04.440 --> 13:05.900
Have you done anything bad

13:06.000 --> 13:07.030
recently?

13:07.500 --> 13:09.930
Your disaster is coming soon.

13:09.960 --> 13:11.330
Wh-What are you talking about?

13:11.330 --> 13:12.280
He can tell that?

13:12.360 --> 13:13.790
Your bloody disaster

13:14.270 --> 13:15.360
is coming soon!

13:15.720 --> 13:16.720
Bah!

13:16.910 --> 13:17.510
I'll smash your darn stall

13:17.510 --> 13:18.510
today—

13:18.510 --> 13:18.870
It's close.

13:18.870 --> 13:19.130
I...

13:20.270 --> 13:20.960
I'll smash it!

13:20.960 --> 13:22.160
It's getting closer.

13:23.540 --> 13:24.850
[Zhu Taijian]

13:24.630 --> 13:25.150
Shi Wen!

13:25.360 --> 13:26.390
Give my money back!

13:26.390 --> 13:27.510
I'll smack you to death!

13:27.510 --> 13:28.480
They really came.

13:28.480 --> 13:29.790
See, wasn't I right?

13:30.600 --> 13:31.600
Give back my money!

13:31.600 --> 13:32.330
Give it back!

13:32.550 --> 13:33.410
I have no money!

13:33.910 --> 13:35.110
You haven't paid yet!

13:35.510 --> 13:36.170
Okay, okay.

13:36.390 --> 13:37.320
Don't rush!

13:37.510 --> 13:38.750
One by one!

13:38.910 --> 13:40.440
Come, line up!

14:06.550 --> 14:07.440
You are here.

14:08.280 --> 14:09.360
I thought you had

14:09.390 --> 14:11.120
run back to the Central Plains.

14:11.120 --> 14:12.030
Why did you run?

14:13.000 --> 14:14.460
I'm asking you why you ran.

14:14.630 --> 14:16.030
Are the mounted bandits that formidable?

14:16.030 --> 14:17.030
You've got me.

14:19.030 --> 14:20.480
You're fast, Lu.

14:21.030 --> 14:22.430
You got them before I did.

14:24.240 --> 14:25.390
Wh-What's going on?

14:26.510 --> 14:28.710
We need to find a place
for him to rest up.

14:28.790 --> 14:30.650
He's been poisoned by a scorpion.

14:45.000 --> 14:46.390
D-Don't kill me!

14:46.870 --> 14:48.200
I'm just a commoner.

14:48.600 --> 14:49.440
I'm penniless

14:49.670 --> 14:50.870
and my life is short.

14:51.270 --> 14:52.670
I-I just bought a coffin.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.660
I really don't know anything.

14:55.200 --> 14:55.960
Heroes,

14:56.200 --> 14:56.750
please,

14:57.120 --> 14:58.120
spare my life.

14:59.440 --> 15:00.770
No one wants to kill you.

15:01.630 --> 15:02.160
I ask you,

15:02.570 --> 15:03.720
was there a group of

15:03.750 --> 15:06.010
Central Plains people with you earlier?

15:08.080 --> 15:09.410
Central Plains people?

15:10.200 --> 15:11.150
No.

15:11.600 --> 15:12.390
Think again.

15:13.390 --> 15:14.200
Yes, yes.

15:14.630 --> 15:15.870
It's those

15:16.150 --> 15:17.320
Central Plains laborers.

15:17.320 --> 15:17.720
Right.

15:18.080 --> 15:20.200
They helped me carry the coffin.

15:20.600 --> 15:22.000
But when they heard

15:22.030 --> 15:23.360
your horses,

15:24.030 --> 15:25.230
everyone scattered.

15:25.270 --> 15:26.080
I don't know

15:26.910 --> 15:28.480
where they went.

15:40.000 --> 15:40.790
Boss,

15:41.080 --> 15:41.960
are you hot?

15:43.360 --> 15:44.440
Just say what you want.

15:44.440 --> 15:45.700
With the sun so bright,

15:46.240 --> 15:47.630
no one will come out.

15:48.790 --> 15:49.790
Shall we close up?

15:50.630 --> 15:51.870
You brat.

15:52.030 --> 15:52.880
Look at

15:52.910 --> 15:53.960
what time it is.

15:54.120 --> 15:55.450
And you want me to close?

15:55.520 --> 15:56.910
Are you intentionally preventing me

15:56.910 --> 15:57.970
from making money?

15:58.030 --> 15:59.790
The problem is no one's coming.

16:00.390 --> 16:02.720
You won't make money
even if you stay open.

16:03.150 --> 16:04.030
You bastard!

16:04.510 --> 16:05.600
If there's no work,

16:06.000 --> 16:07.000
can't you wipe the tables,

16:07.000 --> 16:07.800
mop the floor,

16:07.870 --> 16:09.200
or find something to do?

16:09.960 --> 16:10.510
Fine.

16:11.030 --> 16:12.090
I'll listen to you.

16:16.200 --> 16:16.910
Boss!

16:17.150 --> 16:18.390
There are customers!

16:19.600 --> 16:20.630
There are customers?

16:20.630 --> 16:21.360
Quick, count—

16:21.360 --> 16:22.420
how many there are.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.600
One, two, three...

16:25.670 --> 16:26.730
Do dead ones count?

16:58.840 --> 17:00.100
Is the hot water ready?

17:00.480 --> 17:01.030
Almost.

17:03.000 --> 17:03.660
Let me do it.

17:03.910 --> 17:04.640
Give it to me.

17:04.920 --> 17:05.520
Thank you.

17:29.240 --> 17:30.590
It's quite cool and shady ahead.

17:30.590 --> 17:31.070
Senior.

17:31.480 --> 17:32.640
Go sit and rest for a while.

17:32.640 --> 17:34.030
I'll go fetch some water.

17:34.030 --> 17:35.110
Then I'll go start a fire

17:35.110 --> 17:36.710
and heat up some flatbreads.

18:24.830 --> 18:25.630
What's wrong?

18:26.110 --> 18:26.640
Nothing.

18:27.400 --> 18:29.550
Senior, did you make this yourself?

18:31.070 --> 18:31.400
Yes.

18:34.350 --> 18:35.550
I am Xin Mei from Xin Xie Manor.

18:35.550 --> 18:36.750
May I know your name, Senior?

18:36.750 --> 18:37.530
It's Lu Qianqiao.

18:37.530 --> 18:41.460
♪ Honor and disgrace;
rumors and prejudice ♪

18:38.200 --> 18:39.260
Qian as in millions

18:39.310 --> 18:40.770
and Qiao as in arbor trees.

18:41.850 --> 18:43.070
Since you consider me your senior,

18:42.260 --> 18:45.660
♪ Everyone has their own take ♪

18:43.640 --> 18:44.840
I will not let you die.

18:46.070 --> 18:47.440
I don't need you to go through any danger.

18:46.290 --> 18:50.120
♪ Fingers coated in blood
and disasters brought about ♪

18:48.350 --> 18:50.110
It'll save me a lot of trouble
if you could

18:50.110 --> 18:51.310
master the Fish Drinking Technique soon.

18:50.140 --> 18:53.380
♪ Were never what I wanted ♪

18:53.070 --> 18:54.030
Lu Qianqiao.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.730
What kind of person are you?

19:05.880 --> 19:06.510
It's mine!

19:07.750 --> 19:08.590
It's mine.

19:08.960 --> 19:09.620
Here you go.

19:11.270 --> 19:12.870
Hairbands are like threads,

19:13.240 --> 19:14.300
connecting karma.

19:15.070 --> 19:16.960
Since it fell into your hands,

19:16.960 --> 19:19.270
it means we are destined to meet.

19:20.160 --> 19:22.310
Let me read your fortune for you.

19:23.000 --> 19:23.550
No need.

19:23.880 --> 19:25.210
I don't believe in this.

19:26.640 --> 19:28.720
Whether you believe it or not
is your business,

19:28.720 --> 19:31.000
but whether I read it or not
is my business.

19:31.000 --> 19:32.460
I don't have money for you.

19:33.750 --> 19:35.400
We disciples of the Crazy Daoist

19:35.400 --> 19:36.920
from Dongting Mountain

19:37.590 --> 19:38.990
only talk about destiny,

19:39.350 --> 19:40.160
not money.

19:51.790 --> 19:52.850
What are you doing?

19:53.030 --> 19:53.960
Physiognomy.

19:54.310 --> 19:56.040
You can do that just by looking.

19:56.550 --> 19:57.400
It's physiognomy—

19:57.400 --> 19:58.350
not just reading faces.

19:58.350 --> 19:59.510
Physiognomy covers a lot,

19:59.510 --> 20:00.310
including...

20:00.880 --> 20:01.480
looks,

20:01.720 --> 20:02.590
facial features,

20:02.590 --> 20:03.850
bones, and palm lines.

20:03.960 --> 20:06.590
They are all things
I have to observe for physiognomy.

20:06.590 --> 20:07.440
Reading faces

20:07.550 --> 20:10.030
can reveal good and bad luck,

20:10.270 --> 20:12.470
but Miss, your Hongluan Star is active.

20:12.790 --> 20:15.030
The Hongluan Star falls on your brow bone

20:15.030 --> 20:17.290
and the radiance can be seen in your eyes.

20:17.680 --> 20:19.920
If I am guessing it right,

20:20.960 --> 20:23.400
there is a tree shadow
in your Hongluan Star.

20:23.400 --> 20:24.240
This person must

20:24.240 --> 20:26.510
be related to arbor trees.

20:46.830 --> 20:48.030
Your brow bone is cool

20:48.550 --> 20:50.410
with a slight bulge in the middle.

20:50.960 --> 20:53.750
You are missing someone.

20:54.110 --> 20:55.480
And this person

20:55.640 --> 20:57.590
has countless ties with you.

20:58.160 --> 20:59.440
Your feelings for him

20:59.790 --> 21:01.120
are quite complicated.

21:01.400 --> 21:03.200
Moreover, this person

21:03.310 --> 21:05.040
also has a deep destiny with me.

21:05.590 --> 21:07.070
It will be very difficult

21:08.240 --> 21:09.350
for you to find him.

21:10.270 --> 21:10.800
However,

21:11.310 --> 21:12.160
rest assured.

21:12.920 --> 21:15.000
You are blessed by the Hongluan Star.

21:15.640 --> 21:17.200
As long as you have him on your mind

21:17.200 --> 21:18.600
you will definitely meet

21:19.200 --> 21:20.400
who you want to see.

21:30.110 --> 21:30.680
Senior.

21:31.310 --> 21:31.880
Senior.

21:32.880 --> 21:33.440
Senior!

21:35.830 --> 21:36.440
Sheng...

21:37.160 --> 21:38.020
What happened?

21:51.750 --> 21:52.810
Confusion Powder?

21:58.640 --> 22:00.110
Oh no. We've been tricked.

22:03.200 --> 22:03.790
Sir, Sir.

22:04.510 --> 22:04.880
Sir.

22:04.900 --> 22:05.930
Please hold up.

22:06.960 --> 22:07.400
Sir,

22:07.680 --> 22:09.480
please come with me for a moment.

22:09.590 --> 22:10.190
Come over.

22:10.550 --> 22:11.350
What's wrong?

22:12.030 --> 22:12.550
Sir,

22:12.880 --> 22:14.080
you can't put a coffin

22:14.200 --> 22:15.550
in the lobby of my inn.

22:16.550 --> 22:17.750
It's an empty coffin.

22:18.400 --> 22:19.640
Even an empty one won't do.

22:19.640 --> 22:21.160
Look, it's such a large coffin—

22:21.160 --> 22:22.240
so big and heavy.

22:22.500 --> 22:23.400
It's an inauspicious sight

22:23.400 --> 22:24.400
in the lobby.

22:24.640 --> 22:26.750
How am I supposed to do business?

22:28.030 --> 22:29.110
You don't have any other guests

22:29.110 --> 22:30.170
in this inn anyway.

22:31.440 --> 22:32.300
How about this?

22:32.430 --> 22:34.760
Could you put this coffin
in the backyard?

22:35.000 --> 22:35.640
Master!

22:35.720 --> 22:36.640
You can move it there then.

22:36.640 --> 22:37.960
How can I move it?

22:38.750 --> 22:39.610
-Master!
-Sir.

22:39.640 --> 22:40.920
Don't hold things back.
We have a life to save.

22:40.920 --> 22:41.790
The hot water is ready.

22:41.790 --> 22:42.070
I...

22:42.310 --> 22:42.640
I...

22:43.160 --> 22:43.560
Hey...

22:45.720 --> 22:47.030
What's their problem?

22:52.680 --> 22:53.400
I've sealed

22:53.400 --> 22:54.600
his arms' meridians.

22:54.960 --> 22:55.550
But this

22:55.720 --> 22:57.880
can only delay the spread of the poison.

22:57.880 --> 22:59.480
To detoxify him completely,

22:59.480 --> 23:00.610
we need medication.

23:00.750 --> 23:01.830
What medicine do you need?

23:01.830 --> 23:03.360
The Dragon Subduing Grass.

23:03.400 --> 23:04.110
In the middle of nowhere,

23:04.110 --> 23:05.270
where are we supposed to find that?

23:05.270 --> 23:06.070
Dragon Subduing Grass

23:06.070 --> 23:07.000
usually grows in

23:07.030 --> 23:08.490
dark places in the desert.

23:08.550 --> 23:10.270
It's most commonly found
in places under stone walls

23:10.270 --> 23:11.510
that haven't seen sun for a long time.

23:11.510 --> 23:12.770
What does it look like?

23:30.400 --> 23:31.530
The water is boiled.

23:32.000 --> 23:34.060
-Give it to me.
-Where should I put it?

23:42.070 --> 23:43.070
I'll go right now.

23:43.110 --> 23:43.910
Wait a minute.

23:44.310 --> 23:45.590
It's too dangerous for you to go alone.

23:45.590 --> 23:46.520
I'll go with you.

23:47.790 --> 23:48.790
Let me go with you.

23:49.070 --> 23:50.240
After all, I know more herbs

23:50.240 --> 23:51.400
than you do.

23:51.880 --> 23:52.400
Huh!

23:52.750 --> 23:54.720
That's like telling me
to take up this job.

23:54.720 --> 23:55.240
I'll go.

23:56.000 --> 23:57.060
You all are clumsy.

23:57.350 --> 23:58.510
If you get bitten by another scorpion,

23:58.510 --> 24:00.160
there won't be a second coffin for you.

24:00.160 --> 24:01.480
If you're going, I'll go too.

24:01.480 --> 24:03.410
Stay here and don't cause trouble.

24:04.440 --> 24:04.970
Let's go.

24:11.960 --> 24:12.510
Sir,

24:12.680 --> 24:14.000
are you going out on a long journey?

24:14.000 --> 24:15.240
The coffin has already been put

24:15.240 --> 24:16.550
in the backyard for you.

24:16.550 --> 24:17.200
Shouldn't you settle

24:17.200 --> 24:18.640
the bill?

24:19.350 --> 24:20.070
Don't ask me.

24:20.070 --> 24:21.280
I'm just a laborer.

24:21.320 --> 24:22.350
Go find those nerds in there.

24:22.350 --> 24:22.960
You...

24:26.310 --> 24:27.440
Filthy poor

24:27.640 --> 24:29.040
but has quite the temper.

24:29.240 --> 24:29.880
Exactly.

24:30.960 --> 24:32.000
What are you looking at?

24:32.000 --> 24:32.880
Are you blind?

24:33.030 --> 24:34.350
Don't you know to close the door?

24:34.350 --> 24:35.880
You want to eat sand?

24:36.200 --> 24:36.830
Go!

24:37.350 --> 24:37.880
Quick!

24:43.880 --> 24:44.590
Innkeeper!

24:44.830 --> 24:46.030
More guests are here.

24:46.240 --> 24:47.290
More guests?

24:47.350 --> 24:48.950
No coffins this time, right?

24:54.820 --> 24:56.030
Please come in.

24:56.030 --> 24:56.490
Please.

24:56.790 --> 24:57.310
Please.

24:58.550 --> 24:59.010
Please.

25:00.000 --> 25:00.530
This way.

25:01.880 --> 25:03.440
Have a seat.

25:10.680 --> 25:11.460
What are you staring at?

25:11.460 --> 25:13.270
Hurry up and clean it for the guests.

25:13.270 --> 25:13.920
Hurry!

25:19.640 --> 25:20.590
Shoo!

25:21.400 --> 25:23.030
This chair is definitely clean.

25:23.030 --> 25:24.000
Please sit.

25:30.440 --> 25:30.960
Master.

25:31.310 --> 25:33.480
Ever since my master
moved into the new house,

25:33.480 --> 25:35.070
he has nightmares every night.

25:35.070 --> 25:36.160
Sometimes we also hear

25:36.160 --> 25:37.240
a woman crying.

25:37.510 --> 25:40.970
We suspect we've encountered
something from the underworld.

25:41.750 --> 25:42.270
You've found

25:42.270 --> 25:43.310
the right person.

25:44.030 --> 25:44.960
Our Master Qian

25:45.110 --> 25:48.030
learned from
the Crazy Taoist of Dongting Mountain.

25:48.030 --> 25:49.200
He's best

25:49.960 --> 25:51.110
at eliminating demons

25:51.110 --> 25:52.840
and turning bad luck into good.

25:53.840 --> 25:55.500
Do you see that person behind?

25:56.350 --> 25:57.360
He looks like a human,

25:57.360 --> 25:58.160
but actually,

25:58.240 --> 25:59.200
he's not.

26:01.190 --> 26:02.230
He is

26:02.310 --> 26:04.240
a pig demon from Heifeng Mountain.

26:04.400 --> 26:05.480
He eats humans.

26:05.960 --> 26:07.640
Influenced by our Master Qian,

26:07.640 --> 26:09.880
he volunteered to follow him and practice—

26:09.880 --> 26:11.680
and now, he has taken human form.

26:12.400 --> 26:13.660
Pardon my disrespect.

26:14.960 --> 26:16.310
He is harmless.

26:17.240 --> 26:17.960
So,

26:18.110 --> 26:19.370
your master's matter—

26:19.790 --> 26:21.590
just leave it to our Master Qian.

26:21.640 --> 26:22.240
All right.

26:23.030 --> 26:24.680
Besides eliminating demons,

26:24.680 --> 26:26.590
we can also help you
look at the feng shui

26:26.590 --> 26:27.720
to ensure your master's

26:27.720 --> 26:28.200
3...

26:28.720 --> 26:30.400
no, 5 generations of peace.

26:30.960 --> 26:31.960
Thank you so much.

26:32.510 --> 26:33.790
No problem.

26:47.510 --> 26:47.960
Run!

27:06.310 --> 27:06.910
It's over.

27:07.750 --> 27:08.750
I miscalculated.

27:09.110 --> 27:09.980
How could the person she's traveling with

27:09.980 --> 27:11.440
be from the immortal sect?

27:17.240 --> 27:18.300
Where's the money?

27:22.270 --> 27:22.880
Here.

27:34.150 --> 27:34.880
This is mine.

27:36.480 --> 27:37.200
In the future,

27:37.200 --> 27:37.860
don't let me

27:38.200 --> 27:40.130
catch you swindling people again.

27:46.830 --> 27:48.160
I didn't miscalculate.

27:48.350 --> 27:49.550
She is a noble person.

27:52.070 --> 27:52.800
Fortunately

27:53.590 --> 27:55.450
she's not from the Tianyuan Sect.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.220
This poison is fierce.

27:59.440 --> 28:00.400
I don't know if he can hold on

28:00.400 --> 28:01.510
until they return with the medicine.

28:01.510 --> 28:02.270
Lyu

28:03.070 --> 28:04.070
won't die, right?

28:04.510 --> 28:05.110
Well...

28:05.720 --> 28:06.650
it's hard to say.

28:07.550 --> 28:08.160
You...

28:08.920 --> 28:09.510
You guys—

28:10.200 --> 28:12.030
can't you wish me well?

28:12.920 --> 28:14.350
-He's awake.
-He's awake.

28:14.350 --> 28:15.000
Master Lu,

28:15.440 --> 28:17.770
your medical skills are truly brilliant.

28:18.310 --> 28:19.640
Come, let me have a look.

28:19.880 --> 28:20.270
Okay.

28:23.440 --> 28:24.040
The poison

28:24.310 --> 28:26.000
is only temporarily suppressed.

28:26.000 --> 28:27.590
But to completely detoxify it,

28:27.590 --> 28:29.270
we still need the Dragon Subduing Grass.

28:29.270 --> 28:30.000
Before that,

28:30.020 --> 28:30.590
you can't feed him

28:30.590 --> 28:31.400
anything.

28:32.110 --> 28:34.030
You can only give him a little water.

28:34.030 --> 28:35.160
I'll remember that.

28:38.310 --> 28:39.240
Enjoy your meal.

28:44.110 --> 28:44.680
Are you

28:44.880 --> 28:46.740
just eating or staying the night?

28:47.310 --> 28:48.710
We're staying the night.

28:48.880 --> 28:49.720
Clear out

28:50.400 --> 28:52.200
all the superior rooms here.

28:53.110 --> 28:54.110
How unfortunate.

28:54.310 --> 28:54.920
Our small inn

28:54.920 --> 28:56.380
only has 2 superior rooms.

28:56.480 --> 28:57.510
One of them

28:57.880 --> 28:58.210
is...

28:58.550 --> 28:59.750
is already occupied.

28:59.920 --> 29:01.380
Then tell them to get lost.

29:02.480 --> 29:04.590
I'm afraid that's not appropriate.

29:08.240 --> 29:09.170
Don't be afraid.

29:09.640 --> 29:10.830
Our Dharma King

29:11.160 --> 29:12.490
is a reasonable person.

29:13.400 --> 29:15.000
Try discussing it with them.

29:15.510 --> 29:17.720
What if they're willing?

29:19.880 --> 29:20.400
Then...

29:20.590 --> 29:22.750
Then I'll go up and ask.

29:29.000 --> 29:29.660
I'll go ask.

29:36.240 --> 29:37.480
Guests in the room,

29:37.720 --> 29:38.920
please open the door.

29:39.310 --> 29:39.770
Guests—

29:41.510 --> 29:42.690
I have a small matter

29:42.750 --> 29:44.550
I'd like to discuss with you.

29:45.880 --> 29:46.480
What is it?

29:47.310 --> 29:48.400
So, here's the thing.

29:48.400 --> 29:49.350
There are some
distinguished guests downstairs

29:49.350 --> 29:50.590
who would like to switch rooms

29:50.590 --> 29:52.790
with you.

29:53.160 --> 29:54.720
Would you be...

29:55.240 --> 29:56.880
They're asking for the moon.

29:56.880 --> 29:57.880
In their dreams.

29:58.030 --> 29:58.880
Dream on.

29:58.960 --> 30:00.000
We are not switching.

30:00.000 --> 30:00.720
Miss,

30:01.000 --> 30:02.160
don't be so angry.

30:02.240 --> 30:03.640
To show their sincerity,

30:04.270 --> 30:05.240
they specifically

30:05.240 --> 30:06.500
brought out this money

30:06.550 --> 30:07.310
as a

30:07.750 --> 30:09.590
compensation for you all.

30:09.750 --> 30:11.070
It's not about compensation.

30:11.070 --> 30:12.100
We were here first.

30:12.100 --> 30:13.900
And one of us is severely injured

30:13.920 --> 30:14.750
and has difficulty moving.

30:14.750 --> 30:15.960
That's such a small amount of money—

30:15.960 --> 30:16.880
how stingy.

30:17.400 --> 30:18.110
If it were me,

30:18.110 --> 30:20.000
I would be embarrassed
to take that out.

30:20.000 --> 30:22.440
You all should listen to my advice.

30:22.810 --> 30:23.200
Sure.

30:23.200 --> 30:23.740
Well—

30:24.680 --> 30:25.010
Sure?

30:26.000 --> 30:26.680
This gentleman

30:26.680 --> 30:27.960
is quite generous.

30:28.030 --> 30:29.240
Thank you, Sir.

30:30.720 --> 30:31.480
Prepare

30:31.790 --> 30:32.920
another room for us.

30:33.480 --> 30:34.200
Of course.

30:34.520 --> 30:35.410
Your room

30:35.440 --> 30:36.920
has already been prepared.

30:36.920 --> 30:38.250
It's on the first floor.

30:39.110 --> 30:39.510
Okay.

30:40.140 --> 30:41.200
Allow us to pack up.

30:42.680 --> 30:43.510
If there's nothing else,

30:43.510 --> 30:44.960
I'll take my leave.

30:45.270 --> 30:46.200
Leave the money.

30:46.640 --> 30:47.240
The money?

30:48.510 --> 30:49.740
Look at my memory.

30:50.200 --> 30:51.400
Here you go.

30:53.030 --> 30:54.400
Even a little bit helps.

30:54.680 --> 30:55.610
Come take a look.

30:55.640 --> 30:56.840
We've got good stuff.

30:57.680 --> 30:58.510
-I'm off.
-Take care.

30:58.510 --> 30:59.270
Come, eat.

30:59.380 --> 31:00.240
Have some meat.

31:01.590 --> 31:02.190
Thank you.

31:02.240 --> 31:03.170
Enjoy your meal.

31:04.110 --> 31:05.510
This place is worth coming to.

31:05.510 --> 31:05.970
Senior.

31:11.510 --> 31:11.840
Here.

31:14.240 --> 31:15.240
Let's just eat it.

31:26.750 --> 31:27.270
Sirs,

31:27.440 --> 31:28.900
are you eating or staying?

31:29.350 --> 31:30.440
Do you have plain water?

31:30.440 --> 31:31.300
I'd like a bowl.

31:31.350 --> 31:32.080
Plain water?

31:33.720 --> 31:34.650
It's 5 wen a bowl.

31:35.000 --> 31:35.800
So expensive?

31:37.550 --> 31:38.880
What about egg noodles?

31:39.200 --> 31:39.920
Also 5 wen.

31:40.440 --> 31:41.440
How can you...

31:42.680 --> 31:43.510
Are you three

31:43.510 --> 31:44.440
eating or not?

31:44.550 --> 31:45.000
Yes!

31:51.480 --> 31:52.480
Bring us one bowl.

31:52.720 --> 31:53.310
One bowl?

32:05.960 --> 32:07.270
There are no seats left.

32:07.270 --> 32:08.400
Let's share a table.

32:23.110 --> 32:24.370
It tastes really good.

32:25.310 --> 32:25.840
Eat more.

32:26.590 --> 32:27.270
Ladies,

32:27.640 --> 32:29.200
which sect are you from?

32:29.790 --> 32:31.960
What are you doing in North Xiang?

32:33.200 --> 32:35.260
Seeking refuge with your relatives?

32:36.480 --> 32:37.720
Are you here on business

32:37.720 --> 32:38.650
or for vacation?

32:42.830 --> 32:43.790
I'm guessing

32:44.350 --> 32:46.210
you are here looking for someone.

32:48.960 --> 32:50.240
Since you're not speaking,

32:50.240 --> 32:51.500
I'll take that as a yes.

32:52.590 --> 32:53.440
To be honest,

32:54.070 --> 32:55.310
I'm familiar with

32:55.480 --> 32:57.000
the 36 regions of North Xiang.

32:57.000 --> 32:58.110
If you want to find someone,

32:58.110 --> 32:59.770
you have to go to Phoenix City.

33:00.440 --> 33:02.350
It's the most bustling place.

33:02.750 --> 33:03.880
Highly accessible,

33:03.960 --> 33:05.760
it's also the hub of North Xiang.

33:10.000 --> 33:11.590
If you are going to Phoenix City,

33:11.590 --> 33:13.960
we might as well travel together.

33:23.400 --> 33:25.110
Do you know why,
even though you tricked me,

33:25.110 --> 33:27.040
I didn't make it difficult for you?

33:27.790 --> 33:29.320
I had so much money in my bag,

33:29.550 --> 33:30.880
but when you knocked me out,

33:30.880 --> 33:32.080
you only took 2 taels.

33:32.640 --> 33:34.240
You still have a conscience.

33:35.160 --> 33:37.030
It seems we are destined to meet, Miss.

33:37.030 --> 33:39.230
A liar with a conscience is still a liar.

33:39.350 --> 33:40.810
Whatever your purpose is,

33:41.200 --> 33:42.260
stop following us.

33:43.310 --> 33:43.750
Sheng,

33:43.960 --> 33:44.490
let's go.

33:54.270 --> 33:55.670
Why are you looking at me?

34:00.030 --> 34:00.550
Eat up.

34:02.130 --> 34:02.580
Come.

34:17.670 --> 34:18.550
I don't think

34:18.570 --> 34:19.830
they are here after us.

34:21.550 --> 34:23.150
Those two ladies are fierce.

34:23.880 --> 34:25.210
But it doesn't look like

34:26.920 --> 34:28.050
they want to kill us.

34:29.400 --> 34:31.070
What if it's a stalling tactic?

34:31.070 --> 34:33.110
That they make us drop our guard first

34:33.110 --> 34:34.969
then go back for reinforcements?

34:36.550 --> 34:37.440
That makes sense.

34:37.440 --> 34:38.900
What sense does that make?

34:39.070 --> 34:40.150
Who are the reinforcements?

34:40.150 --> 34:40.550
You?

34:41.070 --> 34:41.510
You?

34:41.840 --> 34:42.480
Or me?

34:43.230 --> 34:44.880
That girl carrying dual swords

34:44.880 --> 34:46.590
could take on 10 of us.

34:47.110 --> 34:48.239
Does she really need

34:48.710 --> 34:50.000
to play tricks on us?

34:51.840 --> 34:53.100
That also makes sense.

34:53.280 --> 34:54.139
So what do we do?

34:55.000 --> 34:55.760
Keep going?

34:57.150 --> 34:57.590
Yes.

34:57.760 --> 34:58.290
Let's go.

35:08.630 --> 35:09.080
Oh no.

35:09.510 --> 35:10.430
They are here.

35:22.440 --> 35:23.360
Why did you stop?

35:23.360 --> 35:24.070
We are still 20 li away

35:24.070 --> 35:25.000
from Xutuo City.

35:25.150 --> 35:26.210
Let's take a break.

35:27.190 --> 35:28.250
Dismount and rest.

35:28.440 --> 35:30.700
We'll set off in an incense stick of time.

35:41.510 --> 35:42.440
Rest on the spot.

35:42.800 --> 35:44.320
We'll set off in an incense stick of time.

35:44.320 --> 35:45.070
-Yes.
-Yes.

35:53.280 --> 35:54.940
Don't worry too much, Senior.

35:55.110 --> 35:56.890
This time, not only our Tianyuan Sect,

35:56.890 --> 35:58.000
Lingji Mountain and Sun Moon Cavern

35:58.000 --> 35:59.130
have also sent
many immortal sect disciples

35:59.130 --> 36:00.190
to intercept them.

36:00.590 --> 36:02.230
These few demonic cultivators

36:02.230 --> 36:03.510
cannot cause any big troubles.

36:03.510 --> 36:05.030
We are catching a bunch of ordinary people

36:05.030 --> 36:06.360
with such a large scale?

36:07.300 --> 36:08.960
They are not ordinary people.

36:09.030 --> 36:10.880
They are really good
at manipulating people's minds.

36:10.880 --> 36:11.960
They're just like the plague.

36:11.960 --> 36:13.480
They spread wherever they go.

36:13.480 --> 36:14.230
I heard that Wushuang Society

36:14.230 --> 36:15.760
only had over 10 people at first.

36:15.760 --> 36:17.400
Now it has gradually grown stronger.

36:17.400 --> 36:18.880
There are people who believe in them

36:18.880 --> 36:20.360
in various states and counties.

36:20.360 --> 36:21.840
Not only do they preach secretly,

36:21.840 --> 36:23.280
but they also gather to make trouble.

36:23.280 --> 36:25.960
Local governments are having a headache
because of them.

36:25.960 --> 36:27.290
This Goddess Wushuang—

36:27.480 --> 36:29.230
isn't she the Goddess of Craftsmanship?

36:29.230 --> 36:30.200
They are

36:30.230 --> 36:30.920
rotten demonic hearts

36:30.920 --> 36:31.630
with

36:31.630 --> 36:32.880
deity skin.

36:33.360 --> 36:35.160
Over the years,
they scatter throughout the world,

36:35.160 --> 36:36.110
causing many commoners

36:36.110 --> 36:38.440
to lose their minds
and enter the demonic path.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.900
They are utterly lawless.

36:40.590 --> 36:41.110
So,

36:41.710 --> 36:43.110
we cannot be soft on them.

36:43.320 --> 36:44.630
It's for the commoners of the world

36:44.630 --> 36:46.090
and for our immortal sect.

36:53.550 --> 36:54.350
There's news.

36:54.920 --> 36:55.450
Let's go.

37:00.840 --> 37:01.200
Here.

37:01.630 --> 37:02.230
Thank you.

37:11.440 --> 37:11.880
Miss!

37:11.880 --> 37:12.280
Quick!

37:13.280 --> 37:13.880
Ladies!

37:14.360 --> 37:15.630
Help! Help!

37:15.920 --> 37:17.570
Please help. Let us on the boat.

37:17.570 --> 37:18.630
You still dare to chase us.

37:18.630 --> 37:20.190
You're really seeking death.

37:20.190 --> 37:20.710
Miss, Miss.

37:20.710 --> 37:22.550
We are being hunted by enemies.

37:22.840 --> 37:24.710
Saving a life brings infinite merit.

37:24.710 --> 37:26.440
Saving 3 lives brings merit
equal to building...

37:26.440 --> 37:27.670
16, 17, 18...

37:28.360 --> 37:29.760
Anyway, thank you, Miss.

37:31.000 --> 37:32.330
There's no time. Quick!

37:32.360 --> 37:33.510
-Get on the boat quickly!
-Thank you!

37:33.510 --> 37:34.110
Hurry!

38:15.360 --> 38:17.250
Tell us. Who exactly are you?

38:17.630 --> 38:18.600
We are just

38:18.630 --> 38:20.430
poor wanderers making a living.

38:20.880 --> 38:21.610
Still lying?

38:22.110 --> 38:22.800
Okay, okay.

38:23.230 --> 38:24.360
I'll tell the truth.

38:24.880 --> 38:25.960
What kind of grudge

38:26.360 --> 38:28.290
do you have with the Tianyuan Sect?

38:29.960 --> 38:32.560
You know the people
from the Tianyuan Sect too?

38:32.880 --> 38:33.880
Is it weird

38:34.320 --> 38:35.190
for us cultivators to know

38:35.190 --> 38:36.280
people from the Tianyuan Sect?

38:36.280 --> 38:38.230
But what did you 3 ordinary people do

38:38.230 --> 38:39.030
that is attracting

38:39.030 --> 38:40.280
so many people from the Tianyuan Sect

38:40.280 --> 38:41.350
to hunt you down?

38:41.440 --> 38:43.280
We didn't really do anything.

38:46.480 --> 38:47.630
We just

38:48.320 --> 38:50.710
took a book from Lingji Mountain before.

38:51.110 --> 38:51.630
Took?

38:52.710 --> 38:53.570
You mean stole.

38:55.030 --> 38:56.490
How can you put it that way?

38:56.800 --> 38:58.440
Knowledge belongs
to everyone in the world.

38:58.440 --> 39:00.360
There's no distinction
between yours and mine.

39:00.360 --> 39:00.760
No distinction.

39:00.760 --> 39:01.960
It's just a book.

39:02.400 --> 39:04.230
We originally wanted to copy it.

39:04.480 --> 39:05.810
But we didn't have time.

39:06.190 --> 39:07.120
We were planning

39:07.400 --> 39:08.590
to return that book.

39:10.000 --> 39:12.070
If you stole a book from Lingji Mountain,

39:12.070 --> 39:13.630
why is the Tianyuan Sect hunting you?

39:13.630 --> 39:14.830
We don't know either.

39:14.880 --> 39:15.920
Maybe they are just
sticking their noses

39:15.920 --> 39:17.650
into other people's business.

39:18.150 --> 39:18.880
Anyway, no matter

39:18.880 --> 39:19.880
what kind of grudge you have,

39:19.880 --> 39:20.630
stop following us

39:20.630 --> 39:21.590
from now on.

39:22.670 --> 39:23.200
Let's go.

39:23.290 --> 39:23.660
I...

40:02.840 --> 40:03.550
Why would

40:04.190 --> 40:05.070
this ship appear in

40:05.070 --> 40:06.880
the arid and waterless North Xiang?

40:06.880 --> 40:08.000
The hull of this ship

40:08.000 --> 40:09.730
is made of teak from Piao State.

40:10.360 --> 40:11.400
This kind of wood

40:11.710 --> 40:13.190
is solid, durable,

40:13.550 --> 40:15.150
and highly anti-corrosive.

40:15.510 --> 40:17.070
When we humans build ships,

40:17.440 --> 40:19.070
we use century-old teak.

40:20.230 --> 40:21.590
Looking at this ship,

40:22.070 --> 40:22.920
it has been abandoned here

40:22.920 --> 40:24.720
for probably hundreds of years.

40:24.950 --> 40:26.430
When this ship was built,

40:26.460 --> 40:27.470
the teak used

40:27.960 --> 40:29.960
must have been a thousand years old.

40:32.430 --> 40:33.960
Forgive us, immortal lady.

40:34.190 --> 40:36.920
There is only one way
to the hinterland of North Xiang.

40:36.920 --> 40:38.510
We won't bother you.

40:40.110 --> 40:40.760
Why would

40:41.030 --> 40:42.760
this ship appear in the desert?

40:43.280 --> 40:44.360
The nearest sea is

40:44.380 --> 40:45.980
a 2-month journey from here.

40:46.000 --> 40:47.200
How was such a big ship

40:47.280 --> 40:48.340
transported here?

40:49.880 --> 40:51.940
You may not know this, immortal lady.

40:52.000 --> 40:53.200
This is not a sea ship.

40:53.480 --> 40:54.110
This is

40:54.590 --> 40:57.150
a tower ship that can fly in the sky.

40:57.800 --> 40:59.030
It wasn't

40:59.030 --> 41:00.230
transported from anywhere else.

41:00.230 --> 41:02.510
It fell from the sky.

41:04.150 --> 41:05.190
Ships can't fly.

41:05.590 --> 41:07.520
Only immortals have that ability.

41:07.960 --> 41:09.290
Thousands of years ago,

41:09.510 --> 41:10.590
with the exquisite craftsmanship

41:10.590 --> 41:11.840
of our human ancestors,

41:11.840 --> 41:13.700
let alone building flying ships,

41:14.030 --> 41:15.190
even indestructible

41:15.190 --> 41:15.920
automatons,

41:16.150 --> 41:17.960
cannons with a range of over 100 zhang,

41:17.960 --> 41:19.820
and super-capacity spatial bags

41:20.150 --> 41:21.360
were a piece of cake.

41:22.960 --> 41:24.360
What are you laughing at?

41:24.630 --> 41:25.430
Spatial bags?

41:25.800 --> 41:28.030
Those are legendary treasures
of the immortals.

41:28.030 --> 41:29.630
Who said spatial bags are...

41:30.110 --> 41:30.960
Spatial bags

41:31.110 --> 41:33.000
were made by our human ancestors.

41:35.440 --> 41:36.030
It was a highly skilled

41:36.030 --> 41:37.590
female artisan.

41:37.800 --> 41:39.130
She ascended to godhood

41:41.360 --> 41:42.510
through her craftsmanship.

41:42.510 --> 41:44.370
She was titled Goddess Wushuang.

41:44.960 --> 41:46.620
That was a thousand years ago.

41:46.630 --> 41:47.070
Of course,

41:47.070 --> 41:47.930
you can't say

41:47.960 --> 41:49.620
she wasn't human just because

41:49.710 --> 41:50.970
she became a god later.

41:51.410 --> 41:52.230
When she created

41:52.230 --> 41:53.960
these miraculous inventions,

41:54.360 --> 41:55.490
she was still human—

41:55.800 --> 41:56.330
a mortal.

41:57.110 --> 41:59.550
Please forgive us.

41:59.840 --> 42:00.900
Please forgive us.

42:08.960 --> 42:11.120
[Qianyan Cavern]

42:11.390 --> 42:13.270
[Soul Lantern Hall]

42:29.280 --> 42:31.760
Congratulations on emerging
from seclusion, Father!

42:31.760 --> 42:34.820
Congratulations on emerging
from seclusion, Father!

42:43.030 --> 42:43.960
Gui is dead.
